OL,3,CWorth the wait: Why this year's
OL,4,Cstrawberries are sweeter than ever
OL,6,FThe British strawberry season is
OL,7,Ffinally underway, two weeks late -
OL,8,Fafter unseasonably cold, wet weather
OL,9,Fled to slower .
OL,11,FBut experts say the harvest is worth
OL,12,Fthe wait - as the slowed growth has
OL,13,Fled to larger and more flavourful
OL,14,Fstrawberries.
OL,16,FProtected under polytunnels, the crops
OL,17,Fdid not suffer damage from the lack of
OL,18,Fwarmth and sunlight. Rather, the more
OL,19,Fgradual growth has fortified the
OL,20,Fplants, allowing them to support
OL,21,Fbigger, juicier berries.
