OL,3,CWorth the wait: Why this year's
OL,4,Cstrawberries are sweeter than ever
OL,6,F"It will be a fantastic year for
OL,7,FBritish strawberries," says Nick
OL,8,FMarston, the Chairman of British Berry
OL,9,FGrowers - the industry body which
OL,10,Frepresents 95% of berries supplied to
OL,11,FUK supermarkets.
OL,13,FIt's been the eighth wettest winter on
OL,14,Frecord for the UK, following a series
OL,15,Fof storms which battered the nation.
OL,17,FThe arrival of spring saw further
OL,18,Fdownpours, with England and Wales
OL,19,Frecording more than 150% of their
OL,20,Faverage monthly rainfall.
