OL,6,FBut although that rain caused delays
OL,7,Fin the season, it has also led to more
OL,8,Fgood news for strawberry fans this
OL,9,Fsummer.
OL,11,FFresh berries - such as strawberries,
OL,12,Fraspberries, blueberries and
OL,13,Fblackberries - continue to be the most
OL,14,Fpopular fruit with Brits.
OL,16,FAndmean that the UK is now self-
OL,17,Fsufficient for the whole summer
