OL,6,FBut British Berry Growers say that
OL,7,Fdespite high global demand for British
OL,8,Fstrawberries, exports have dropped 79%
OL,9,Fin volume since 2020.
OL,11,FThis is due to , including health
OL,12,Fcertificates and additional customs
OL,13,Fpaperwork - as well as delays in
OL,14,Fshipments which can affect product
OL,15,Fquality.
